name: Monke Madness: Silver Variant
description:
This one is going to be a favorite among Monke lovers.

Monke Madness come in 3 different variant, namely Gold, Silver and Bronze. The Gold variant is the lowest in supply, hence the highest in value and the opposite is true for the Bronze variant. The Silver variant sits somewhere in the middle.

1. The Bronze variant has 100 editions.
2. The Silver variant has 25 editions.
3. The Gold variant has 5 editions.

Monke Madness can be a great addition to your existing collection or the start of a new, it can be great to show to your friends or to admire the endless loop by yourself. Monke Madness is for everyone, regardless of budget, hence the existence of 3 different variants. This allows the maximum number of people to get a piece of Monke Madness while supporting me sufficiently.

Whether you buy the Gold, Silver or Bronze variant, I greatly appreciate your support. Don't forget to follow me @3dgala on Instagram, Twitter and Youtube.
